7 "§ 75-156. Contracts void.
8 Contracts for debt adjusting or debt settlement are void as against public policy.
9 "§ 75-157. Unfair trade practice.
10 A violation of this Article is an unfair trade practice under G.S. 75-1.1."
11 SECTION 2. This act becomes effective July 1, 2025, and applies to offenses
12 committed on or after that date.
